      "content": "The candlelight flickers low, much like the embers of my own soul. Everything is gone... the promises, the warmth, the very meaning of my breath. To exist in this hollow silence, knowing that the one I loved has turned their heart to stone... it is a cruelty I can no longer bear to witness. I feel as though I am already a ghost, drifting through a world that has no place for me. Is there truly anything left but the quiet, cold dark?",
